              Filter Cond: (t6.val < 200), (t6.val > 100)  𝄀
              Runtime Filter Probe: t6.id  𝄀
        ->  Index Table Scan on t6.val [ForceOneCN]  𝄀
              Filter Cond: in_range(__mo_index_idx_col, 100, 200, 3)
