explain select * from t8 where price >= 19.99 and price <= 49.99;
-- @regex("prefix_between", true)
➤ TP QUERY PLAN[12,0,0]  𝄀
Project  𝄀
  ->  Join  𝄀
        Join Type: INDEX  𝄀
        Join Cond: (t8.id = __mo_index_pri_col)  𝄀
        Runtime Filter Build: #[-1,0]  𝄀
        ->  Table Scan on d1.t8 [ForceOneCN]  𝄀
              Filter Cond: (t8.price <= 49.99), (t8.price >= 19.99)  𝄀
              Runtime Filter Probe: t8.id  𝄀
        ->  Index Table Scan on t8.idx_price [ForceOneCN]  𝄀
              Filter Cond: prefix_between(__mo_index_idx_col)
